_text = "As I approach the tunnel entrance, I can feel some of my memories returning to me. They aren't clear, but I can feel that the impact of these moments are precious to me.\n\nUpon entering, I begin to smell odors coming from the tunnel. I smell a mix of the salty ocean water, with a tang of fresh hay.\n\nHowever, these smells seem to be coming from opposite directions. Do I explore the ocean to my left or focus my attention on the hot wheat fields to my right?"

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, Monitor, MonitorNo, MonitorYes, OceanMemoryRoom, SouthernAlbertaMemory, false)